<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
	 </p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
	<span style="font-family:verdana, geneva, sans-serif;">Badger Meter attended AWWA's Annual</span></p>
<p style="margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0;padding:0;">
